{
  "stem": "15578.7",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Do you think your survival had anything to do with the fact that you and your brother were together?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Well, we did stick together, as plain as this.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That's all.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, I remember he stares, sometime would come in his eyes, when I did work in the kitchen in Ohrdruf, and he did come over after the shift and look at me into my room and the way I looked.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I looked so nice and not nourished and so you understand.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he did-- he was the happiest man.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Very good.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The relationship was very good.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Before the war and after the war.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] No.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, not at.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm the-- I'm the same person.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] No.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, because, to be honest with you, we didn't talk so much.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But lately, we've talked about.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In the beginning, we didn't.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Maybe it wasn't right.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because they start to growing, and they went to school, and they are learning something.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So that's the reason they ask me questions.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Like the little one, Shoshanah, said Zayde, when you were in camp, what did you do?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I said I had to work.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she said, if you didn't want to work.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I said they could shoot me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They could kill me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And you know what she mentioned to me?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She said I rather they shoot me and I go to heaven [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and not to do what they want.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Eh, 11 years, she will be.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I would like to.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
